  "texts": [
    "Additionally, biomimetic designs inspired by the human olfactory system can greatly improve these devices.",
    "For instance, arrays of chemically selective receptors can mimic the combinatorial coding of odors, enhancing both specificity and robustness.",
    "Furthermore, the demand for real-time data processing is increasingly critical, particularly for applications like environmental monitoring, medical diagnostics, and wearable olfactory interfaces (Al Mamun and Yuce 2019).",
    "However, deploying olfactory analysis systems on portable devices remains challenging due to the computational intensity associated with large-scale machine learning models.",
    "This situation necessitates the development of lightweight, energy-efficient AI models optimized for edge computing platforms."
